605
00:54:57,820 --> 00:54:58,860
 U spavaču sobu.

606
00:54:58,860 --> 00:55:00,000
 U spavaču sobu.

607
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:01,080
 Da, da, da, apsolutno.

